    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行美洲 ECM 联席主管因调查离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/deutsche-bank-s-co-head-of-americas-ecm-left-amid-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德意志银行前美洲股票资本市场联席主管 Beau Bohm 于 4 月份离职，原因是他涉嫌与下属有私人关系，目前正在接受调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/deutsche-bank-s-co-head-of-americas-ecm-left-amid-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:18:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Endeavour Mining 将取代 Smurfit Kappa 成为富时 100 指数成分股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/endeavour-mining-to-replace-smurfit-kappa-in-ftse-100-index-ly65tye4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金矿商 Endeavour Mining Plc 借助贵金属价格上涨，在英国蓝筹指数中占据一席之地，取代包装公司 Smurfit Kappa Group Plc，后者在与美国竞争对手 WestRock Co. 合并后退出了该指数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/endeavour-mining-to-replace-smurfit-kappa-in-ftse-100-index-ly65tye4</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:17:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官支持迪士尼拒绝基金对代理文件的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/judge-sides-with-disney-in-refusing-fund-demand-for-proxy-files</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特拉华州一名法官得出结论，华特迪士尼公司无需交出有关其与 ValueAct 资本管理公司的关系以及这位激进投资者在该娱乐巨头董事会激烈的代理权争夺战中所扮演的角色的记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/judge-sides-with-disney-in-refusing-fund-demand-for-proxy-files</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选消息不断升温，华尔街警惕拜登退场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿关于总统乔·拜登是否放弃竞选连任的激烈辩论正在蔓延到华尔街，交易员们正在将资金转移到美元、美国国债和其他可能受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫影响的资产上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Piper Sandler 放弃标普 500 指数目标，称练习毫无意义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/piper-sandler-drops-s-p-500-target-says-practice-is-poor-form</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Piper Sandler &amp; Co. 的宏观研究团队将不再发布标准普尔 500 指数年底的单一数字预测，称这是一种与客户沟通的低效方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/piper-sandler-drops-s-p-500-target-says-practice-is-poor-form</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：就业报告发布前标普 500 指数创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列弱于预期的经济报告强化了美联储今年开始降息的理由后，华尔街交易员推高了股市，而债券收益率则下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
